{"total":3,"pageSize":10,"pageCount":1,"data":[{"title":"调教Hexo之个性化","slug":"调教Hexo之个性化","date":"2018-03-16T10:56:41.000Z","updated":"2018-03-16T11:38:12.616Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/调教Hexo之个性化.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":"http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo-config/layout.png","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>本来想自己的hexo搞得个性化一点，然而难受的是，一搜索hexo个性化，全是next主题的各种骚操作，但是看看我们的主题，简直日了狗好吧。<br>没办法，不想用那种烂大街的东西，就只好自己多找点插件用用了，不是前端工程师的悲哀。。。。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><em>我的主题为<a href=\"https://github.com/HeskeyBaozi/hexo-theme-lite\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">lite</a>，以下配置均依照该主题设置，但是我说的方法都是通用的</em></p>\n<h2 id=\"七牛图床同步插件\"><a href=\"#七牛图床同步插件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"七牛图床同步插件\"></a>七牛图床同步插件</h2><p>使用<a href=\"https://github.com/gyk001/hexo-qiniu-sync\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">该插件</a>之后，可以直接将图片放到本地，然后通过 </p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\">{% qnimg imageFile %} \n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>直接引用</p>\n<h2 id=\"站点收录\"><a href=\"#站点收录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"站点收录\"></a>站点收录</h2><h3 id=\"本地配置\"><a href=\"#本地配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"本地配置\"></a>本地配置</h3><p>在根目录下运行</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> hexo-generator-baidu-sitemap --save\n<span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> hexo-generator-sitemap --save\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>然后在根目录的配置文件下添加</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\" spellcheck=\"true\"># 自动生成sitemap</span>\nsitemap:\n  path: sitemap.xml\nbaidusitemap:\n  path: baidusitemap.xml\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>还有记得修改url为自己的域名<br>重新生成后就可以在public目录里面看到sitemap.xml和baidusitemap.xml文件了。</p>\n<h3 id=\"引擎收录\"><a href=\"#引擎收录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"引擎收录\"></a>引擎收录</h3><blockquote>\n<p>很不幸的告诉你，上面配置的百度站点地图完全是白费的23333<br>因为github阻止了百度的爬虫，所以你在百度站长平台认证时，通不过的。<br>如果你死都想让百度收录。。。。骚年，我浪费了我整整1天来告诉你——–死了这条心吧<br>网上的答案不外乎：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>不使用github的pages，转而使用其他的替代pages。然而国内的coding：对个人博客会有5秒跳转，除非你在你的博客中加入coding的标识（mmp，乘火打劫，而且图标还丑的一批，而且这个跳转机制有时还会让爬虫失效。）。码云：不支持自定义域名。国外的gitlab：日您！还需要用CI/CD在服务器部署，我弄了大半天都没弄出来！</li>\n<li>使用域名服务器进行海外海内分别解析。比如把国内解析到coding上，国外的解析到github上。但是cloudflare说：臣妾做不到啊！如果你想换用国内的域名服务器，那么https手动和您再见。如果你想自己用免费的ssl证书，那么请使用自己的vps（不就是钱吗，微笑）。我曾经用过do做自己的hexo服务器，但是这又是一个大坑啊啊啊啊啊，我第一次配置也花了1天多啊。我现在还是回到了github，就是省心，老年人玩不动了。。。。。。</li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n<p>不过安慰自己的就是，现在开发人员谁不是用google。恩，所以我们来看看谷歌收录吧。<br>首先登录google站长<a href=\"https://www.google.com/webmasters/#?modal_active=none，然后`添加属性`，输入域名。\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://www.google.com/webmasters/#?modal_active=none，然后`添加属性`，输入域名。</a><br>验证方法有多种。如果使用文件验证，请把文件放到你的主题目录文件下的source文件夹中，这样生成的时候会一起生成。<br>但是我使用的主题，url后面都会带一个/#,所以验证文件的url和google期望的不一样，于是我使用的是标签验证。找到主题目录下的layout目录，我的里面只有一个文件，然后修改文件，加入标签即可。<br>最后在抓取中找到<code>站点地图</code>添加即可</p>\n<h2 id=\"添加点击效果\"><a href=\"#添加点击效果\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"添加点击效果\"></a>添加点击效果</h2><ol>\n<li>确定主题的js文件所在。可以找到\\themes\\lite\\layout目录下的文件，我的是index.ejs，打开后查看已有的js路径<img src=\"http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo-config/layout.png\">\n比如这里有<code>&lt;script type=text/javascript src=/static/js/manifest.9c14e4c25ff8a4ffed18.js&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</code>这样的代码，然后我在<code>\\themes\\lite\\source\\static\\js</code>下找到了该js文件。每个主题的js存放目录都不一样，需要自己去找。</li>\n<li>将<a href=\"https://github.com/Neveryu/Neveryu.github.io/blob/master/js/src/love.js\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">love.js</a>添加到js存放目录，如<code>\\themes\\lite\\source\\static\\js</code></li>\n<li>修改\\themes\\lite\\layout目录下的文件，如index.ejs，在<code>&lt;/body&gt;</code> 标签之前添加如下代码（上方我给出的图片中我已经添加了）<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token operator\">--</span> 页面点击小红心 <span class=\"token operator\">--</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script type<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"text/javascript\"</span> src<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/js/src/love.js\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>重新部署，然后就能看到啦！！！</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"添加2d人物模型\"><a href=\"#添加2d人物模型\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"添加2d人物模型\"></a>添加2d人物模型</h2><p><a href=\"https://github.com/EYHN/hexo-helper-live2d/blob/master/README.zh-CN.md\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">项目地址</a><br>这个文档有中文，安着步骤来一下就成功了，不多说了。</p>\n<h2 id=\"鼠标经过时头像旋转\"><a href=\"#鼠标经过时头像旋转\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"鼠标经过时头像旋转\"></a>鼠标经过时头像旋转</h2><p>打开你的网页，然后右键检查元素，找到头像所在的js文件<br>看到右边样式一栏，点击js文件或者鼠标停在上面就可以看到js文件，然后本地搜索js文件，打开，添加如下代码。代码来自<a href=\"https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000009544924#articleHeader7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">这里</a>（都是针对的Next主题，很无奈，然后对前端也不熟悉，摸索半天才找出几个能行的）</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\"><span class=\"token class\">.avatar</span><span class=\"token attribute\">[data-v-73f77182]</span> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> inline-block<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">4.3</span>rem<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">4.3</span>rem<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">50%</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">box-shadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>px <span class=\"token number\">1</span>px <span class=\"token number\">3</span>px <span class=\"token hexcode\">#fff</span>\n <span class=\"token comment\" spellcheck=\"true\">/* 以上为原文件内容 */</span>\n\n <span class=\"token comment\" spellcheck=\"true\">/* 设置循环动画 [animation: (play)动画名称 (2s)动画播放时长单位秒或微秒 (ase-out)动画播放的速度曲线为以低速结束 \n    (1s)等待1秒然后开始动画 (1)动画播放次数(infinite为循环播放)] */</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\" spellcheck=\"true\">/* 鼠标经过头像旋转360度 */</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\" spellcheck=\"true\">/* 可以自己调这里的时间参数，改变旋转速度 */</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-transition</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> -webkit-transform <span class=\"token number\">0.7</span>s ease-out<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-moz-transition</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> -moz-transform <span class=\"token number\">0.7</span>s ease-out<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">transition</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> transform <span class=\"token number\">0.7</span>s ease-out<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">img<span class=\"token pseudo-class\">:hover</span> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\" spellcheck=\"true\">/* 鼠标经过停止头像旋转 \n  -webkit-animation-play-state:paused;\n  animation-play-state:paused; */</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\" spellcheck=\"true\">/* 鼠标经过头像旋转360度 */</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rotateZ</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">360</span>deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-moz-transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rotateZ</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">360</span>deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rotateZ</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">360</span>deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\" spellcheck=\"true\">/* Z 轴旋转动画 */</span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@-webkit-keyframes</span> play</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">0% </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rotateZ</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span>deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">100% </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rotateZ</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>-<span class=\"token number\">360</span>deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@-moz-keyframes</span> play</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">0% </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">-moz-transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rotateZ</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span>deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">100% </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">-moz-transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rotateZ</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>-<span class=\"token number\">360</span>deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@keyframes</span> play</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">0% </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rotateZ</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span>deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">100% </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rotateZ</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>-<span class=\"token number\">360</span>deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"代码高亮\"><a href=\"#代码高亮\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码高亮\"></a>代码高亮</h2><p>使用<a href=\"https://github.com/ele828/hexo-prism-plugin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">这个插件</a><br>有20多种代码样式，够你爽（滑稽<br>我这里试了几种，给你们放个图<br>atom-dark<br><img src=\"http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo-config/atom-dark.png\"></p>\n<p>base16-ateliersulphurpool.light<br><img src=\"http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo-config/base16-ateliersulphurpool.light\"></p>\n<p>ghcolors<br><img src=\"http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo-config/ghcolors.png\"></p>\n<p>okaidia<br><img src=\"http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo-config/okaidia.png\"></p>\n<p>solarizedlight<br><img src=\"http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo-config/solarizedlight.png\"></p>\n<p>tomorrow<br><img src=\"http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo-config/solarizedlight.png\"></p>\n<p>twilight<br><img src=\"http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo-config/twilight.png\"></p>\n<p>参考：<a href=\"http://shenzekun.cn/hexo%E7%9A%84next%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%AA%E6%80%A7%E5%8C%96%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">hexo的next主题个性化教程:打造炫酷网站</a><br><a href=\"http://fengdi.org/2017/08/10/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E7%99%BE%E5%BA%A6%E5%92%8CGoogle%E6%94%B6%E5%BD%95.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hexo博客提交百度和Google收录</a></p>\n","text":"本来想自己的hexo搞得个性化一点，然而难受的是，一搜索hexo个性化，全是next主题的各种骚操作，但是看看我们的主题，简直日了狗好吧。<br>没办法，不想用那种烂大街的东西，就只好自己多找点插件用用了，不是前端工程师的悲哀。。。。我的主题为lite，以下配置均依照该主题设置，","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"Hexo搭建教程","slug":"Hexo搭建教程","date":"2018-03-16T07:52:52.000Z","updated":"2018-03-16T11:03:21.349Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Hexo搭建教程.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":"http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo/dns.png","content":"<p>我的hexo又双叒叕被我玩坏了。。。。。。<br>博客这东西我就喜欢折腾，但是不喜欢写。。。<br>玩过hexo，后来还玩过worldpress，然而博客一篇没写（笑哭<br>hexo玩坏之后我都是直接删除然后重新建一个，本来就没几篇博客<br>现在打算好好的开一个hexo，然后开始写博客了（划重点，这是一个flag</p>\n<p>然后先记录一下怎么重装hexo吧，免得以后玩崩了又要找教程（雾</p>\n<h2 id=\"前期准备\"><a href=\"#前期准备\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"前期准备\"></a>前期准备</h2><p>这些安装网上一大把教程，而且官方也有文档</p>\n<ul>\n<li>node.js，默认会安装npm。</li>\n<li>git</li>\n<li>hexo</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"构建本地博客\"><a href=\"#构建本地博客\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"构建本地博客\"></a>构建本地博客</h2><p>hexo有官方文档 <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/setup.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://hexo.io/docs/setup.html</a></p>\n<ol>\n<li>新建一个文件夹，如blog</li>\n<li>进入文件夹，运行命令行（我是用linux下的命令行，当然git命令行也可以），然后输入<code>hexo init</code></li>\n<li>输入 <code>npm install</code></li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"关联github\"><a href=\"#关联github\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"关联github\"></a>关联github</h2><p>打开根目录下的_config.yml文件，修改</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-dash\"><code class=\"language-dash\">deploy:\n  type: git\n  repository: git@github.com:royyoung388/royyoung388.github.io.git\n  branch: master\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>然后运行</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-dash\"><code class=\"language-dash\">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save\nhexo g\nhexo d\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>作用：安装插件；生成本地静态文件；将文件push到github<br>deploy的时候会需要输入密码，免密deploy的<a href=\"ttp://eesly.github.io/2014/10/26/%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8ssh%E7%9C%81%E5%8E%BB%E5%9C%A8hexo-deploy%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">方法</a><br>关于各大仓库的提交插件<a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/deployment.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">在这</a></p>\n<p>这时候你就可以在浏览器输入yourid.github.io（就是你的仓库名）访问你的hexo博客啦！！！</p>\n<h2 id=\"绑定域名\"><a href=\"#绑定域名\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"绑定域名\"></a>绑定域名</h2><p>我使用的域名服务器是cloudflare，有免费的https服务，但是它的dns设置和其他一般的dns设置不同，有坑。。。。。<br>添加两条A记录，分别指向192.30.252.153和192.30.252.154<br>然后添加一条CNAME记录，名字为www，别名是 royyoung388.github.io (就是仓库名)<br><img src=\"http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo/dns.png\"><br>然后为了使用https，在pagerule下添加如下几条rule<br><img src=\"http://p5n2a03cb.bkt.clouddn.com/static/images/hexo/rules.png\"><br>配置完域名解析后<br>进入source目录，新建一个文件CNAME（注意没有后缀名），写入你的域名。注意有www和没有www的情况！我的域名服务器是有www前缀的，如果CNAME里面没有www前缀，会出现重定向的死循环！<br>然后访问你的域名就可以看到啦！访问github也会被重定向到你的域名的！(当然，也有可能要等待一段时间，等待dns生效）</p>\n<h2 id=\"修改主题\"><a href=\"#修改主题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"修改主题\"></a>修改主题</h2><p>前往官网<a href=\"https://hexo.io/themes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">themes</a>，然后找到你喜欢的主题。按照人家给出的教程安装即可。考虑到每个主题的配置都是有差别，而且别人的文档也挺齐全的，我就不在赘述了</p>\n<p>到此整个hexo的基本搭建就ok啦！</p>\n","text":"我的hexo又双叒叕被我玩坏了。。。。。。<br>博客这东西我就喜欢折腾，但是不喜欢写。。。<br>玩过hexo，后来还玩过worldpress，然而博客一篇没写（笑哭<br>hexo玩坏之后我都是直接删除然后重新建一个，本来就没几篇博客<br>现在打算好好的开一个hexo，然后","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[{"name":"hexo","slug":"hexo","count":1,"path":"api/categories/hexo.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"hexo","slug":"hexo","count":1,"path":"api/tags/hexo.json"}]},{"title":"Hello World","slug":"hello-world","date":"2018-03-15T10:23:04.474Z","updated":"2018-03-15T10:23:04.474Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hello-world.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>Welcome to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\"><a href=\"#Quick-Start\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Quick Start\"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id=\"Create-a-new-post\"><a href=\"#Create-a-new-post\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Create a new post\"></a>Create a new post</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ hexo new <span class=\"token string\">\"My New Post\"</span>\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Writing</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Run-server\"><a href=\"#Run-server\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Run server\"></a>Run server</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ hexo server\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Server</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Generate-static-files\"><a href=\"#Generate-static-files\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Generate static files\"></a>Generate static files</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ hexo generate\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Generating</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Deploy-to-remote-sites\"><a href=\"#Deploy-to-remote-sites\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Deploy to remote sites\"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ hexo deploy\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Deployment</a></p>\n","text":"Welcome to Hexo! This is your very first post. Check documentation for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the ","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]}]}